ckEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p>La propiedad <code><strong>Animation</strong></code><strong><code>.effect</code></strong> de la&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a> obtiene y establece el efecto objetivo de una animación. El efecto objetivo puede ser un objeto efecto de un tipo basado en <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffectReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, como <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, o <code>null</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>effect</em> = <em>Animation</em>.effect;\n\n<em>Animation</em>.effect = <em><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffectReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></em></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un objeto <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffectReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> que describe el efecto de animación objetivo para la animación, o <code>null</code> para indicar que el efecto no está activo.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-effect\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation.effect' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Editor's draft.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.effect","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffectReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad Animation.effect de la  Web Animations API obtiene y establece el efecto objetivo de una animación. El efecto objetivo puede ser un objeto efecto de un tipo basado en AnimationEffectReadOnly (en-US), como KeyframeEffect (en-US), o null.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.effect","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.effect","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/effect","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/effect/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect","title":"Animation.effect"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.effect - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}